ANNOUNCEMENTS (06): OIE SPECIAL WEBSITE ON 90TH ANNIVERSARY
***********************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
http://www.isid.org

Date: 2 Feb 2014 [accessed 23 May 2014]
Source: OIE press release [edited]
http://www.oie.int/en/for-the-media/press-releases/2014/oie-90th-aniversary


The World Organisation for Animal Health (OIE) has launched a special website to commemorate its 90th anniversary http://www.90.oie.int.

Information on dates and facts about the history of the organisation during 9 decades and its progress in standards, expertise, transparency and solidarity can be found on the website.

Search can be done by:
- main themes;
- monthly dossiers;
- dates and keywords;
- an interactive map about the OIE, Member Countries and network;
- a monthly newsletter with facts and dates.

The latest news and events of the organisation are also available in the website in 3 different languages (French, English and Spanish).

--
