[The special website is available at http://www.90.oie.int.

The 82nd General Session of the World Assembly of OIE Delegates will be held from 25 to 30 May 2014, bringing together representatives of 178 OIE member states and observers from international organisations that have signed an official agreement with the OIE, as well as other international and regional organisations and invited guests.

The World Assembly of OIE Delegates establishes the policies of the OIE and supervises their implementation. See more at http://www.oie.int/eng/Session2014/information.htm. - Mod.CRD]
